name: IECColourManagement
title: IEC 61966-2-1: Colour measurement and management - Part 2-1: Colour management - Default RGB colour space - sRGB

contact.name: International Electrotechnical Commission; 3 rue de Varemb√©, PO Box 131, CH-1211 Geneva 20, Switzerland

description:
IEC 61966-2-1:1999 is the official specification of sRGB. It provides viewing environment, encoding, and colorimetric details.

For more information, please see https://webstore.iec.ch/publication/6168
